These are changes for CSM 4.0.
Including non-ECEF sensor models, alternative reference frames and multi-point.
ObjectSpaceRasterGM replaces RasterGM.
ObjectSpacePointCloudGM replaces PointCloudGM.
All references to "Ground" in APIs are replaced by "ObjectSpace".
ProjectionParamters provides alternative viewing geometries as an argument to imageToObjectSpace.
CoordinateReferenceSystem allows specification of unique CRS and supports ECEF, ECI and LSR.
These changes are not backward compatible with CSM 3.X.
